# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
1. If number of components != 1 --> return 0
2. Else if #components = 1, and articulation point exists --> return 1
3. Else return 2
4. Imp observation: Max possible answer is 2 in any case. As even if complete mesh, remove two adjacent nodes of corner cell to make it disconnected.

