# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
We will check if we have not 1 island then return 0 , else we will try to make every 1 cell 0 then check if we have more than 1 islands if we have then we return 1 else in end we return 2 .
# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(N^4)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: O(N^2)
