1 1 &nbsp;1

3. a point connecting with no other points(an island it self)
0 &nbsp;0&nbsp; 0
0 (1) 0
0&nbsp; 0&nbsp; 0

(The 1 surrended in brackets should be test). 

If there are 0 or more than 1 islands,
