# Intuition
First element is always fixed , now take rest elements and divide array in two arrays and repeat same process for each array. 
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->

# Approach
Take first element as root, not divide array in two parts which contains lesser elments and greater elements than the root node respectively and put in new array in same order. 
